{"tid":2511751,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"安心院薰染同一拳打邊個贏","createTime":"2021-05-01T06:50:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T13:05:14.000Z","uid":79471,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bb42e0a32306635a1dd784f49712ab532f67d911","tid":2511751,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T06:50:01.000Z","msg":"1京2858兆519億6763萬3865個技能應該贏到限制器開放<br />\n<img src=\"https://p1.pstatp.com/origin/pgc-image/f9ffe113851f4cadacf951c37ce6a67e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp1.pstatp.com%2Forigin%2Fpgc-image%2Ff9ffe113851f4cadacf951c37ce6a67e.png&h=8b7b67cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"596338150d5c0281ad1cc8d0f9fd71f13a075ba0","tid":2511751,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T06:51:09.000Z","msg":"到宇宙誕生為止，我等了三兆年<br />\n然後到地球誕生為止，我等了一百億年<br />\n到類似生命的東西誕生為止，我又再等了六億年<br />\n直到人類出現為止，途中看著恐龍的興亡<br />\n我又等了五億五千萬年<br />\n和同類的相遇雖說是最近，也已經是一百五十年前的事情了<br />\n可以說是不放過任何分身仔細搜尋的結果吧。<br />\n和讓我充滿期待的人類，第一次見面是在五年前<br />\n但是結果他也辜負了我的期待。<br />\n與目高相遇是在那兩年之後<br />\n今天則是在那三年之後，所以---<br />\n我等待今天的到來，<br />\n已經花了3兆4021億9382萬2311年0287天了---"},{"pid":"76ee058ad38fb89431e3f38d9f2781562171f533","tid":2511751,"uid":14719,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T06:52:02.000Z","msg":"佢連自己個故事啲人都贏唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7139fe8d823ae9d483ddade2db00aa830d804875","tid":2511751,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76ee058ad38fb89431e3f38d9f2781562171f533","tid":2511751,"uid":14719,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T06:52:02.000Z","msg":"佢連自己個故事啲人都贏唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T06:53:03.000Z","msg":"讓賽/唔係正面打"},{"pid":"af7617ccaca2ba2c2ce9787f5ed113998b68eafd","tid":2511751,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76ee058ad38fb89431e3f38d9f2781562171f533","tid":251175